@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        h1, h2 {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #343a40;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            position: relative;
            animation: fadeInDown 1s ease forwards;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease forwards;
        }

        .section {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            animation: slideUp 1s ease forwards;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        @@keyframes fadeIn {
            from

        {
            opacity: 0;
        }

        to {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        }

        @@keyframes fadeInDown {
            from

        {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(-20px);
        }

        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        }

        @@keyframes slideUp {
            from

        {
            transform: translateY(40px);
            opacity: 0;
        }

        to {
            transform: translateY(0);
            opacity: 1;
        }

        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container py-4">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Who We Are</h2>
            <p>Darris is an innovative platform designed to bridge the gap between students and their academic journey at the university. We focus on simplifying the connection between subjects, schedules, academic requirements, and student goals.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>About Darris</h2>
            <p>Darris helps students organize, understand, and plan their academic paths. With intuitive tools, it provides easy access to course materials, recommended study plans, progress tracking, and future academic projections — all tailored to the specific curriculum of each student.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>The Hashemite University</h2>
            <p>The Hashemite University, located in Zarqa, Jordan, is one of the leading public universities in the country. Known for its commitment to academic excellence and innovation, the university provides a nurturing environment for thousands of students in various disciplines. Darris was proudly initiated in collaboration with the vision of enhancing academic experience at The Hashemite University.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
